### 3e. Block Image Upload (mirrors `handleWidgetImageUpload` at lines 539-564)

```js
const handleOpenBlockImagePicker = (blockId) => {
    const input = blockImageInputRefs.current[blockId];
    if (input) {
        input.value = '';
        input.click();
